nk ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mo-thay-con-bo\/#Mo_ve_mot_con_bo_dien\" >M\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t con b\u00f2 \u0111i\u00ean<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mo-thay-con-bo\/#Mo_thay_bo_thi_nen_danh_so_may_cho_may_man\" >M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y b\u00f2 th\u00ec n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y cho may m\u1eafn?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mo-thay-con-bo\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n nay v\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho ch\u00fang ta m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mo-thay-con-bo\/\">m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/a> th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t. V\u1eady h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">sv368<\/a> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u xem li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m l\u00e0nh hay d\u1eef nh\u00e9!<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hinh_anh_cua_con_bo_trong_van_hoa_va_tam_linh\"><\/span><b>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a con b\u00f2 trong v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 t\u00e2m linh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong n\u1ec1n v\u0103n h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ea1i ch\u00fang th\u00ec h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u1ee3ng con b\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u00eau t\u1ea3 v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ec1n v\u0103n minh l\u1edbn. Kh\u1eafp n\u01a1i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e3 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n k\u00ednh lo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n n\u00e2ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh l\u00ean t\u1ea7m m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb th\u1ea7n. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 \u1edf \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 th\u00ec c\u00f3 b\u00f2 tr\u1eafng Nandi l\u00e0m v\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7n Siva, hay \u1edf Ai C\u1eadp th\u00ec th\u1edd ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea7n b\u00f2.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong v\u0103n h\u00f3a Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u00f2 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n, t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c k\u00e9o xe \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e0y. Theo quan ni\u1ec7m x\u01b0a th\u00ec ch\u00fang b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ng\u1ed1c ngh\u1ebfch. Song \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 lo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m, t\u00ednh kh\u00ed hi\u1ec1n l\u00e0nh v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1eefu \u00edch.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00f2 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n c\u00f9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa con ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f4ng d\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xem lo\u00e0i v\u1eadt n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n qu\u00fd gi\u00e1, c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 tr\u00e2n qu\u00fd n\u00f3.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4345\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4345\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4345 size-full\" title=\"m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-1.jpg\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a con b\u00f2 trong v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 t\u00e2m linh\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-1.jpg?v=1736188808 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-1-300x150.jpg?v=1736188808 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-1-768x384.jpg?v=1736188808 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4345\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a con b\u00f2 trong v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 t\u00e2m linh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Y_nghia_viec_mo_thay_con_bo\"><\/span><b>\u00dd ngh\u0129a vi\u1ec7c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 kh\u00e1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a kh\u00e1c nhau. T\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng trong gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng m\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t h\u00e0m \u00fd t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng. Song nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i th\u00ec con b\u00f2 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9, ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f4ng d\u00e2n. Do \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 v\u00f4 t\u00ednh chi\u00eam bao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u00e0i v\u1eadt n\u00e0y th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o t\u1ed1t, t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4346\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4346\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4346 size-full\" title=\"m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-2.jpg\" alt=\"\u00dd ngh\u0129a vi\u1ec7c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-2.jpg?v=1736188808 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-2-300x150.jpg?v=1736188808 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-2-768x384.jpg?v=1736188808 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4346\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u00dd ngh\u0129a vi\u1ec7c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Giai_ma_mot_so_giac_mo_ve_nhung_chu_bo\"><\/span><b>Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa b\u00f2<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh. C\u00f9ng <strong>SV368<\/strong> \u0111i\u1ec3m qua m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1eb1ng sau gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mo_thay_con_bo\"><\/span><b>M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n ng\u1ee7 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 con b\u00f2 th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o cho s\u1ef1 th\u1ecbnh v\u01b0\u1ee3ng, may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac s\u1eafp t\u1edbi trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. B\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c si\u00eang n\u0103ng, nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Song h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd k\u1ef9 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 <\/span><b>m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> g\u1ea7y \u1ed1m th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn, h\u00e3y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mong_thay_con_bo_ruot_minh\"><\/span><b>M\u1ed9ng th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2 r\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00ecnh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 th\u00ec n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ngo\u00e0i th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf m\u00e0 b\u1ecb con b\u00f2 r\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai c\u0169ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi gi\u1ea5c <\/span><b>m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> n\u00e0y th\u00ec c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u stress, m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c. Nh\u1eefng l\u00fac nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec h\u00e3y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, b\u00ecnh \u1ed5n l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m x\u00fac r\u1ed3i t\u1eeb t\u1eeb t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chiem_thay_ban_than_dang_bi_bo_huc\"><\/span><b>Chi\u00eam th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111ang b\u1ecb b\u00f2 h\u00fac<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngo\u00e0i b\u00f2 r\u01b0\u1ee3t ra th\u00ec b\u00f2 h\u00fac ch\u1eafc c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. Song v\u1edbi gi\u1ea5c <\/span><b>m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2 <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">n\u00e0y th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n b\u1ea1n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u00e0 tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh b\u1ea1n \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn h\u01a1n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean h\u00e3y t\u1ef1 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ed3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch h\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ngu_mo_thay_bo_di_vao_nha_cua_minh\"><\/span><b>Ng\u1ee7 m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y b\u00f2 \u0111i v\u00e0o nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ed1t, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n. Tin t\u1ee9c n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i l\u1ed9c, may m\u1eafn ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean m\u1edbi, n\u00f3i chung l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. V\u1eady n\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh th\u00e2n y\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00e3y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 t\u1eeb v\u0169 tr\u1ee5 ngay n\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4347\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4347\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4347 size-full\" title=\"m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-3.jpg\" alt=\"Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa b\u00f2\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-3.jpg?v=1736188809 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-3-300x150.jpg?v=1736188809 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-3-768x384.jpg?v=1736188809 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4347\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa b\u00f2<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mo_thay_ca_mot_dan_bo\"><\/span><b>M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e0n b\u00f2<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c<\/span><b> m\u01a1 th\u1ea7y con b\u00f2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> theo m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e0n mang h\u00e0m \u00fd r\u1eb1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd vi\u00ean m\u00e3n, \u0111\u1ea7m \u1ea5m v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. N\u00f3i chung \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ed1t, t\u00edch c\u1ef1c do \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mo_ve_mot_con_bo_dien\"><\/span><b>M\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t con b\u00f2 \u0111i\u00ean<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac l\u1ea5n \u00e1t l\u00fd tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ecdi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng, h\u00e0nh x\u1eed \u0111\u1ec1u theo b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc n\u00e0o. <\/span><b>M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111i\u00ean l\u00e0 l\u00fac m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o h\u01a1n, th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00f3ng gi\u1eadn m\u00e0 l\u00e0m h\u1ecfng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mo_thay_bo_thi_nen_danh_so_may_cho_may_man\"><\/span><b>M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y b\u00f2 th\u00ec n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y cho may m\u1eafn?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eam bao v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng con b\u00f2 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00f4 may m\u1eafn:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2 <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th\u00ec m\u1ea1nh tay \u0111\u00e1nh 07, 45 v\u00e0 80.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y b\u00f2 r\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 b\u00f2 h\u00fac th\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh 08. 24, 10, 45 v\u00e0 77.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chi\u00eam bao c\u00f3 b\u00f2 \u0111i v\u00e0o nh\u00e0 m\u00ecnh th\u00ec s\u1ed1 04, 28 v\u00e0 65.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng con b\u00f2 \u0111i\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 12, 30 v\u00e0 61.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u1ee7 m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e0n b\u00f2 ghi con 02, 47 v\u00e0 83.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4348\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4348\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4348 size-full\" title=\"m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-4.jpg\" alt=\"M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y b\u00f2 th\u00ec n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y cho may m\u1eafn?\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-4.jpg?v=1736188809 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-4-300x150.jpg?v=1736188809 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-con-bo-4-768x384.jpg?v=1736188809 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4348\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y b\u00f2 th\u00ec n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y cho may m\u1eafn?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c <\/span><b>m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> m\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chia s\u1ebb. Theo d\u00f5i SV368 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecf t\u00fai nhi\u1ec1u lu\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i chi\u00eam bao kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n nay v\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho ch\u00fang ta m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con b\u00f2 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t. V\u1eady h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng sv368 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u xem li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m l\u00e0nh [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4345,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4344","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4344","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json